ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of CARLOS LEITAO of Dorval, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on February 28, 2025, in the place of Monique Jérôme-Forget, C.M., O.Q., whose term has expired.
